=Description=

"With Skills, users can tag themselves and their friends with a variety of skills and interests, whether they involve actual jobs, hobbies or future dreams. The idea is that the tags act as a sort of “social endorsement” tool. With a Chrome or Firefox browser extension, Skills tags can even be viewed directly in your Twitter feed." [http://www.educationdive.com/news/the-death-of-degrees-9-alternative-credentialing-approaches/102618/]
